Class DefaultDnsCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.netty.resolver.dns.DefaultDnsCache
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DnsCache

    public class DefaultDnsCache
extends Object
implements DnsCache
    Default implementation of DnsCache, backed by a ConcurrentMap.
